text.section:
At the time a consumer applies through a facilitator for a refund anticipation loan, the facilitator shall disclose to the consumer, on a form that is separate from the application, in 14 point type, the following:
The fee for the refund anticipation loan, including any fee for tax preparation or other fees charged to the consumer;
The annual percentage rate payable on the refund anticipation loan;
The time within which the proceeds of the refund anticipation loan will be paid to the consumer if the refund anticipation loan is approved;
A legend, centered and in bold capital letters in 18 point type, stating:
The statement:

At the time a consumer applies through a facilitator for a refund anticipation check, the facilitator shall disclose to the consumer, on a form that is separate from the application, in 14 point type, the following:
The fee for the refund anticipation check, including any fee for tax preparation or other fees charged to the consumer;
The time within which the proceeds of the refund anticipation check will be paid to the consumer;
A legend, centered and in bold capital letters in 18 point type, stating:
The statement:
